'''腌面'''是[[廣東|廣東]][[梅州|梅州]]特有的[[客家菜|客家小吃]]。
== 作法 ==
将面条用开水煮熟后捞起，加拌猪油、炸香的蒜仁及葱粒，再配少许鱼露，是客家人喜爱的早餐，常搭配[[三及第汤|三及第汤]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.mzta.gov.cn/info/shi/kjmc/2011/1119/2518.html|title = 腌面|accessdate = |author = |date = 2011-11-19|publisher = 梅州市旅游局|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160702001858/http://www.mzta.gov.cn/info/shi/kjmc/2011/1119/2518.html|archive-date = 2016-07-02|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://mt.sohu.com/20150709/n416481384.shtml|title = 当葡萄酒遇上客家美食(梅县腌面篇)|accessdate = |author = |date = 2015-07-09|publisher = 搜狐}}</ref>

